  <Strings>
    <Section>Story</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>260468</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_320_030_001</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>現在、バンディ将軍率いる部隊は、
東部国境地帯で敵軍と交戦状態に
あります</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Currently General Bundy's unit is positioned in the eastern 
national border area. </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>260468</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_320_030_002</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>戦闘が長期化し、物資確保が
困難となり、部隊は
苦境に立たされており……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Their fight has dragged on therefore forcing the military 
to attack neighboring countries for basic supplies. </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <BubbleId>2</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>260608</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_320_030_003</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>……くそっ……
何やってんだよ……！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>...Crap...! What is this!? </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>260608</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_320_030_004</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>そんな連中、
オレがいれば、
全滅させてやるのに……！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>If I was enlisted in the army I would have killed them all 
already...! </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <BubbleId>2</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>261048</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_320_030_005</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>１３歳の時、
オレは軍人になろうと決めた</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>When I turned 13 I became a soldier. </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>261048</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_320_030_006</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>両親の仇を討ちたかった。
オレにはその選択しかなかった</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I had to revenge my parents. It was by my own volition I 
joined. </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <BubbleId>2</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>261392</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_320_030_007</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>だから、全部、
戦争のせいにすんだな</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>That's right. Everything was the war's fault. </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>261392</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_320_030_008</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>デリス・カーラーンを
滅ぼしたのも全部</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Derris Kharlan's destruction and everything else. </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <BubbleId>2</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>261596</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_320_030_009</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>戦争がなかったら
オレは軍人には
ならなかった</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>If there wasn't any war I wouldn't have needed to become a 
soldier. </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>261596</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_320_030_010</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>デリス・カーラーンも
無事だった</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Derris Kharlan would have been fine. </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <BubbleId>2</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>261596</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_320_030_011</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>おまえのように
自分の可能性を……
夢を追いかけていたはずだ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>You are...that dream of a possibility become true. </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <BubbleId>3</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>262344</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_320_030_012</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>…………</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>... </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
